title: Nishikori Beats Cilic to Reach Japan Open Semifinals
text:
Published By: NYTimes Tennis - Today 
Defending champion Kei Nishikori beat Marin Cilic 3-6, 7-5, 6-3 on Friday to advance to the semifinals of the Japan Open....
